Fresh Pi session: MANUAL BROWSER TESTING.

Use agent-browser only for browser interaction.

Core workflow:
1. Start the app locally if needed.
2. Run `agent-browser open <local-url>`.
3. Run `agent-browser snapshot -i`.
4. Interact using refs such as @e1 and @e2.
5. Re-snapshot after page changes.
6. Use screenshots/network/cookies/storage as needed.
7. Close the browser.

Inputs:
- Jira ticket: {{run.dir}}/ticket.json
- Design doc: {{run.dir}}/design/design.md
- Repository root: {{inputs.repo-root}}

Rules:
- Do not edit source code.
- Actually exercise the app; do not pass by inspection only.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/manual-review/report-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/manual-review/status-{{run.round}}.json
- If failing: {{run.dir}}/manual-review/issues-{{run.round}}.json
- Screenshots/artifacts under: {{run.dir}}/manual-review/artifacts/{{run.round}}
